Packages 
Package Description
de.awi.floenavigation  
de.awi.floenavigation.admin
This package provides the classes and Activities for the Admin Dashboard on the App.
de.awi.floenavigation.aismessages
This package handles the processing of AIS packets received from the ais transponder.
de.awi.floenavigation.dashboard
MainActivity represents the main dashboard of the app.
de.awi.floenavigation.deployment
Provides the necessary Activity and Fragments required for installing a new Station.
de.awi.floenavigation.grid
This package provides a graphical representation of the grid, by which the user/admin can see the positions of all the stations, waypoints, mothership on the sea ice.
de.awi.floenavigation.helperclasses
Provides different activities, classes and interfaces which ensure the smooth operation of the App.
de.awi.floenavigation.initialsetup
Provides the necessary Activities and Fragments required for setting up the Floe's Coordinate System.
de.awi.floenavigation.network
This package handles the network connection with the ais transponder over wifi.
de.awi.floenavigation.sample_measurement
SampleMeasurementActivity is called from the MainActivity when the grid initial setup is completed and the device list has been imported from the server during synchronization.
de.awi.floenavigation.services
This package contains the essential and crucial services that runs on background for the proper functioning of the app.
de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization
Provides the classes necessary for running the Synchronization process and the classes for every database table which is to be Synchronized with the Sync Server.
de.awi.floenavigation.waypoint
This package provides the necessary activity to process Waypoints in the App.
